<p>The current version of Ubuntu Christian Edition supports both 32-bit and 64-bit PCs. Ubuntu Christian edition covers all standard desktop applications from word processing applications, spreadsheet, web server and programming tools.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Along with standard Ubuntu applications, Ubuntu Christian Edition includes the best software available. The latest version contains Xiphos, OpenLP, Quelea, and more.</p>
</blockquote>

